column5: Hey all,  I think we may get the program tonight.  I am possibly the last person alive still paying for these things...  who are the winners?
Unfortunately GSP doesn't fight until next weekend.
Yep, next weekend.  Tonight it is Steve B's brother and another fight with Fedor E and Andrea A.  forrest
Isn't all that "watching big sweaty menzes in clinch" kinda G-A-....?
Only if your calling the fighters "menzes"
The mrs,s dont seem to mind.  As for GSP,I think.he will have his hands full with Penn. Penn is one tough dude.
GSP, may be pound for pound the best fighter out there
No questioning that. Im just saying that Penn is no push over.Be interesting to see if GSP can open him up with a strike game. I have to give the ground game to Penn.
oh yeah, I think its going to be a  great fight

There is an Affliction fight card on tonight.  Starts at 9:00; headliner is Arlovsky vs. Emallianenko.  It's on the dish or Pay Per View. Should be a beauty.  Can't wait to see GSP dominate BJ Penn.  Paul
Yeah, reminds me of the 3rd review in this clip....
I was just trying to get a head start...  Of course I knew it was next weekend....hahahahhahahaa
